text: The Korsør List (Danish: Korsørlisten) is a local political party in Slagelse Municipality, Denmark. ==History== The Korsør List was founded in September 2009 by Dan Nielsen and Henrik Andersen.dinby.dk "Ny politisk liste til kommunalvalget" However, it did not run for the municipal council in 2009. In the 2013 Danish local elections, the list ran with two candidates in Slagelse Municipality, led by Mads Mitchell.Danskfolkeparti.dk "Er ny Korør-Liste et forsøg på vælgerbedrag?" The list received 0.5% of the votes, which was not enough for a seat in the municipal council.Kmdvalg.dk Election results from Slagelse Municipality ==Election results== === Municipal elections === {|class="wikitable" |- ! rowspan="2"| Date ! rowspan="2"| Votes ! colspan="2"| Seats |- ! # ! ± |- ! 2013 | 214 | | New |} ==References== Category:Political parties in Denmark Category:Political parties established in 2009 Category:2009 establishments in Denmark
